Cake Boss is an American reality television series that originally aired on the cable television network TLC. The series premiered on April 19, 2009, and spawned four spin-offs: Next Great Baker, Kitchen Boss, Bake You Rich, and Bakery Boss.

On January 26, 2015, Cake Boss was renewed for two additional seasons, which aired on TLC until 2017. Season 9 premiered on May 18, 2019, with the show moving to TLC's sister network, Discovery Family. The show officially ended on April 11, 2020.

description:
Come one step closer and I will knock his teeth out. #onceuponatimeinhollywood #bradpitt #movie #quentintarantino #perioddrama #showbizdrama #margaretqualley 
Welcome to Los Angeles in 1969 through the unique lens of genius director Quentin Tarantino in Once Upon a Time... in Hollywood. This film is an emotional journey, blending dark humor, nostalgia for Hollywood’s golden age, and the signature surprises that only Tarantino can deliver.

The story revolves around Rick Dalton (played by Leonardo DiCaprio), a fading television star struggling to hold onto his former glory, and his loyal friend and stunt double, Cliff Booth (Brad Pitt). Together, they try to find their footing in a rapidly changing Hollywood, where the spotlight no longer shines as brightly as it once did. Along the way, their lives intertwine with real historical events, including the ominous shadow of the Manson Family—a dark chapter in American history.

Joining the duo, Margot Robbie brilliantly portrays Sharon Tate—the iconic beauty and talent of the 1960s—bringing a radiant and heartfelt energy to the screen. The film isn’t just a tale of careers and friendship; it’s also a loving tribute to cinema, featuring breathtaking visuals that vividly recreate a bygone era.

The soundtrack is an unmissable highlight, with 1960s hits perfectly timed to transport viewers back in time. From dusty bars and dazzling film sets to the sun-drenched streets of L.A., every frame is meticulously crafted. And, as with all of Tarantino’s works, the climax will leave you speechless with twists you’ll never see coming.
Press play to step into a Hollywood that’s both glamorous and chaotic, where dreams and nightmares are separated by a razor-thin line. Don’t forget to leave a comment and share your thoughts after watching!
